			"boundElements": [],
			"updated": 1783260970755,
			"link": null,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "Note:\n• For simplicity, transitions which occur voluntarily or result from conflict resolution\nintervention are not shown. These transitions may follow any of the shown\ntransitions going \"outwards\" (i.e. Member → Volunteer → Visitor →  (No position)) \n• * The \"accepted as Visitor\" transitions from the Volunteer and Member states\nlead to (No position). An active hosting agreement is the only determinant for\nsomeone becoming a Visitor.",
			"fontSize": 28,
			"fontFamily": 6,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "Note:\n• For simplicity, transitions which occur voluntarily or result from conflict resolution\nintervention are not shown. These transitions may follow any of the shown\ntransitions going \"outwards\" (i.e. Member → Volunteer → Visitor →  (No position)) \n• * The \"accepted as Visitor\" transitions from the Volunteer and Member states\nlead to (No position). An active hosting agreement is the only determinant for\nsomeone becoming a Visitor.",
